storyInfo: When a supply and food shortage hits the safe house, the Rhodes Island operators propose to search through the ravaged Infected homes to recover anything that might have avoided confiscation. However, in the process, they are stopped by the guards of the Lord of Long Spring.

attributes.content: Find anything?
attributes.name: Frost

attributes.content: Got something! It's not much, but it's something.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Good work. These provisions, along with the emergency store in the safehouse, should keep us fed for a week, if we stretch it.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: It's getting late. Let's head back.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: ...Someone's coming.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: How many?
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: ...A dozen maybe. Could be mercenaries.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: Hurry! Back to the safehouse!
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Are they still on us?
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: ...Yes.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: That's not good.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: I knew they wouldn't let up.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: We are bound to get sieged if we choose to fight here. Keep retreating.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: What happened?
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: We've got company. Get ready to fight.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Something's not right...
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: ...Hold your fire...
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: Why?
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: ...It's not those mercenaries.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: ...They're Reproba soldiers...
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: Local guards?
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Hold fire!
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Guards, surround the structure! Don't let anyone escape.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Wait a second, are we surrounded?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: ...This isn't good.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Why are the Lord's men encircling us?
attributes.name: Liskarm

attributes.content: Let's have you quiet down for now.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: I want all of you inside to listen up!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: I am the captain of the Long Spring village guard, daughter of the Lord of Long Spring, Picale Tulla.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: I want you all to lay down your weapons and come out nice and easy.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Don't test my patience. You'll regret it.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.text: The imposing Reproba warrior strikes the halberd into the ground with all her might.
And the earth starts to tremble instantly.

attributes.content: Mercenaries. It's always mercenaries.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: You shameless, faithless, virtueless bastards. How much gold did my evil brother give you?
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: You won't get away. I'll crush you. I'll stomp you into dust.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: I'll make you pay for everything you've done.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Once I cut you down, you'll finally understand that no amount of blood money can buy you another life!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Oh! Oh! Are you sure they're here to help?
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: I think they'd rather hang us from the town gate.
attributes.name: Blitz

attributes.content: That's what I'm afraid of.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: There's definitely a misunderstanding here.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Lady Picale.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: I'm a field operator with Rhodes Island, code name Rangers.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: I'm pretty sure Rhodes Island signed a cooperation agreement with your family.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: We're...
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Shut up!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Rhodes Island! Sanctimonious hypocrites!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: My father trusted you! He believed your promises. That's why he agreed to your safehouse.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: And how did you repay him?
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: You kidnapped our people! Robbed them of everything they had! I saw it!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: You're a bunch of treacherous villains!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: If you think for a single second, you'll know that doesn't make any sense.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: If we wanted to pillage the town, why would we still be here?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Don't try to talk your way out of this!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: And who the hell are you?
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: You're standing on my father's land with your guns, and you dare to argue with me?!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: If you're so tough, where have you been all this time?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: You and the Lord's men let those thugs raid the quarantine zone so we had to risk our lives to save the townsfolk in there. What were your precious guardsmen doing then?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: And you still think you can come here and talk a big game with us?
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Settle down. She doesn't seem like the type you can reason with.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Lady Picale!
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: I'm Dr. Miarow, from the Infected quarter! We've met before!
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: ...Right. I know you.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Rhodes Island didn't rob the Infected. I can testify to that! We were forced here by the riots.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: And it's not just me. Any of the Infected here will tell you that.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Lady Picale, I need you to trust me.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: ...I trust you, Doctor. Many people speak highly of you.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Thank you, Lady Picale.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: But I don't trust them!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.text: The imposing daughter of the Lord points forward with her colossal halberd.

attributes.content: It is a grave infraction to enter my father's territory, armed, without permission!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: In light of you protecting my father's subjects...
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: I will pardon you for that infraction.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: As for Rhodes Island! The contract you signed with my father is, as of today, null and void.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: ...Please reconsider.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: There is nothing to discuss!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Long Spring does not need armed foreigners, not even Rhodes Islanders!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: I will gather up the Infected and take them where they belong.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: We don't need you getting involved.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: But...
attributes.name: Liskarm

attributes.content: Alright. Don't speak.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Do not defy the local Lord. We are standing here at Sargon as Rhodes Island operators.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Forty-one, forty-two...
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: Any others?
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: That's all...
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: No problem. We'll get you to safety.
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: Miss Cohen, Mr. Alexsandr.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Thank you for all that you've done.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: No need. We should be thanking you.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Where are you going to go?
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Not sure yet.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: Let's not make it sound so sad.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Maybe we'll meet again someday.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: I'll have to tell you about it next time...
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: *Cough* *cough*... the story of the dog-headed man.
attributes.name: Tachanka

attributes.content: Hahaha... alright.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Doctor, this is for you.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: It's... an Originium Ingot. But I can't...
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Remuneration. For Occphen's leg.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: That was just some basic first aid... it's not worth this much...
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: I think it's worth it. Take it.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Thanks, Mr. Rangers.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: And... thank you all.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Goodbye.
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Something's off.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: I know.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: *Sigh*. I thought caution was the right move, but we ended up with a big misunderstanding.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Who would've thought the captain of the guard would be so difficult?
attributes.name: Liskarm

attributes.content: A muscle-headed moron. We have enough of those at BSW.
attributes.name: Franka

attributes.content: So what do we do?
attributes.name: Liskarm

attributes.content: They seized pretty much everything from the safehouse.
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: At least we're all unharmed. That's what really matters.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Come with us, Mr. Occphen. We'll sign you in at the branch office, then contact the landship and figure out what to do.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: That's really our only option.
attributes.name: Occphen

attributes.content: ...I'm not so sure.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: What do you mean?
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: ...That Picale woman... could she be the one behind all this?
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: The Lord was so slow to act, even as the mercenaries were rounding up the Infected.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: ...And now we've got a captain of the guard, taking everyone away all nice and legally.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: This can't just be a coincidence.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: ...That does make sense.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: ...I'm going to tail them... and see.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: I'm going too.
attributes.name: Ash

attributes.content: No. More hands are more easily seen.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: The rest of you stand by.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: What's the matter?
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: I thought you won't agree with this plan.
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: Avoiding conflicts with the local Lord doesn't mean our hands are tied here. We need to play to the score.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: Some times you need a few tricks to get things working.
attributes.name: Rangers

attributes.content: I see...
attributes.name: Schwarz

attributes.content: Get them all to shelter first, then I want three with me.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: I think there's something happening in the mines.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Understood.
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: Is there enough room left in the shelter?
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Not really. Half of the town's population is already inside.
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: Tell them to move upstairs if necessary. Them can have my father's room.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Is this...really necessary?
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: I don't see anything wrong with it. My father will do the same should he lived.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: ...I see.
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: Don't let your guard down anyway.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: ...Wait, did the lights go out as soon as we left?
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: I don't remember...
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: Out of the way
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Aaah!
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: Gaa...
attributes.name: Originiutant

attributes.content: We're under attack! Protect the civilians!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Where did they come from?!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: What are you waiting for?! Get ready to break through!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: There's too many of them!
attributes.name: Lord's Guard

attributes.content: Take the civilians and get out of here! I'm breaking off!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Come on, you cowardly bandits!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Phew... How many was that?
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Finally.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Lady Picale!
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Doctor! What are y ou doing here?!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Don't go! The Lord's Manor has already been...
attributes.name: Miarow

attributes.content: Doctor!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Drudge!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Get the hell out of here! I'm going to chop your goddamned head off!
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Hahaha... You're loud as you ever were, dear sister.
attributes.name: Drudge

attributes.content: You... You disgusting... I have to kill you.
attributes.name: Picale

attributes.content: Show me what you've got.
attributes.name: Drudge

attributes.text: As the imposing Reproba charges at her brother with shocking speed, she realizes it.
She's fallen right into a trap.
Under the cover of night, behind the crumbling houses, a machine rumbles.
In one second, she feels herself struck dizzy by a ferocious blow, as if slammed right in the face by a boulder launched from a catapult.
In the next second, she falls unconscious.
